{"tid":1929520,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑我嘅自戀人格一直阻住我溝女","createTime":"2020-03-17T03:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T07:09:53.000Z","uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58d2a5fff326c9522e2efa878cbbb9cb1ef4bac9","tid":1929520,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"已經唔止一次就溝到手大家都有好感嘅時候，自己突然間諗埋一邊，無喇喇疑心對方係咪中意自己，甚至突然間好唔想拍拖，於是放咗手<br />\n<br />\n放咗手之後睇返，根本人地就係中意自己，係自己諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有條女個frd之後仲問我做乜鳩，臨溝到又放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣可以消滅嗰個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實唔止感情生活，好多嘢都俾佢控制住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb937e1372cbd3c351f6d7bc36f995f95fc3e491","tid":1929520,"uid":352735,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"呢個到底係自卑人格定自戀人格？"},{"pid":"5b7e5affd841a93955a0e172520bcaae84aa19b5","tid":1929520,"uid":74182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"你真係諗多咗"},{"pid":"a32c578741b635afacdea368697611f6a4d1bd22","tid":1929520,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb937e1372cbd3c351f6d7bc36f995f95fc3e491","tid":1929520,"uid":352735,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"呢個到底係自卑人格定自戀人格？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n不過我一定有自戀人格障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲特徵中到應一應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n測過好高分"},{"pid":"ce4b7d5b0cb741913b265035e1d6af8a48a2d792","tid":1929520,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5aaf14d131e4e52618914a681c5986a745fff9","tid":1929520,"uid":23707